---
title: Roast Beef and Redcurrant Gravy with Roast Potatoes, Blue Cheese Celeriac Gratin & Chorizo Savoy Cabbage
description: We love a good Roast Beef with  Blue Cheese & Chorizo and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roast-beef-and-redcurrant-gravy-3486bb3b-2c0f1f10.jpg
